This project (`roomba-lab`) was developed as a graded coursework submission
for Dr. Yoram Segal's Reinforcement Learning course (Lecture 09 — DDPG).

PERMITTED:
  - Reading and review by course staff and fellow students for grading,
    educational discussion, and methodology study.
  - Forking for personal learning experiments (no academic redistribution).
  - Citation of the methodology (PRDs, layered build, mini-Graphify,
    iterative-adversarial-review pattern) in academic writing.

PROHIBITED:
  - Submission of this code (in whole or substantial part) for credit in
    any other academic course.
  - Commercial use of the simulator, DDPG implementation, or any artefact.
  - Redistribution outside the original course context.

